DeckClock
Copyright 2026 ShowEngineering

DeckClock monitors compatible DJ players and generates LTC/timecode from
their transport data.

This product includes modified portions of python-prodj-link:
https://github.com/flesniak/python-prodj-link

The original python-prodj-link project is licensed under the Apache License,
Version 2.0. A copy of that license is included with this distribution.

Modifications include additional user interface elements, LTC/timecode
generation, audio output support, transport clock handling and application
branding.

